Package kp.company.hibernate

Class HibernateCompany

  • java.lang.Object
    • kp.company.hibernate.HibernateCompany
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Company
    @Repository
@Transactional
public class HibernateCompany
extends java.lang.Object
implements Company
    Hibernate implementation of the Company interface.

    The mappings are defined in "kp_spring01.hbm.xml", located in the root of the class path.

    Note that transactions are declared with annotations and that some methods contain "readOnly = true" which is an optimization that is particularly valuable when using Hibernate (to suppress unnecessary flush attempts for read-only operations).
